data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET WITH UPGRADES!! DON'T MISS OUT!! Location!! Location!! Location!! New Floors and Paint downstairs!! Welcome home!! This spacious and well-maintained home is perfect for any living situation. Whether you are a first-time home buyer, raising a family, or an empty nester, this home would be perfect for you. This townhome features a large living area for family entertainment with gray Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring downstairs, an eat-in Kitchen with a breakfast bar area, and half bath downstairs. Upstairs you'll find two large master suites with high vaulted ceilings and walk-in closets. Step outside to a private backyard with a professionally installed vinyl fence. The HVAC is less than a year old, the water heater is two years old, and the roof is only three years old.
